msgid "5.2.0"
msgstr "5.2.0"

#. Tag: title
#: whatsnew.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's new in this release"
msgstr "Kaj je novega v tej izdaji"

#. Tag: title
#: whatsnew.docbook:9
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bug fixes and enhancements to functionality"
msgstr "Popravki napak in izboljšave funkcionalnosti"

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As with every release, the &kmymoney; development team continues to work "
"hard to make each version better and easier to use in every way. Many bugs "
"have been fixed since the previous stable release of 5.1.3; several areas of "
"the program have seen functional enhancements; but the major noticeable "
"changes from the 5.1 series of releases are in the ledger - more details "
"below."
msgstr ""
"Kot pri vsaki izdaji, &kmymoney; razvojna ekipa še naprej trdo dela, da bi "
"bila vsaka različica boljša in lažja za uporabo v vseh pogledih. Veliko "
"napak je bilo popravljenih od prejšnje stabilne izdaje 5.1.3; več področij "
"programa je bilo funkcionalno izboljšanih; vendar so glavne opazne spremembe "
"glede na serijo izdaj 5.1 v glavni knjigi – več podrobnosti spodaj."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The conversion from using the earlier &kde; libraries to &kde-frameworks; "
"was essentially complete in the early 5.1.x releases, with much of that work "
"behind the scenes and not directly visible to the end user. The general look "
"and feel should continue to remain stable, although some minor changes may "
"be noticeable. In addition, the team has begun to make changes to support "
"the conversion to using Qt6 and KDE6 libraries, which have already started "
"to replace Qt5 and KDE5. With all these changes, the basic functionality of "
"the program remains the same, aside from intentional bug fixes, "
"improvements, and additions."
msgstr ""
"Pretvorba iz uporabe prejšnjih knjižnic &kde; v &kde-frameworks; je bil v "
"bistvu dokončan v zgodnjih izdajah 5.1.x, pri čemer je bilo veliko tega dela "
"v zakulisju in ni bilo neposredno vidno končnemu uporabniku. Splošni videz "
"in občutek bi morala še naprej ostati stabilna, čeprav so lahko opazne "
"nekatere manjše spremembe. Poleg tega je ekipa začela izvajati spremembe za "
"podporo pretvorbe v uporabo knjižnic Qt6 in KDE6, ki sta že začeli "
"nadomeščati Qt5 in KDE5. Z vsemi temi spremembami ostaja osnovna "
"funkcionalnost programa enaka, razen namernih popravkov napak, izboljšav in "
"dodatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In past releases, this section of the manual included a list of many of the "
"specific bug fixes and functional enhancements. However, rather than "
"duplicating that information, you can find it directly in the <ulink url="
"\"https://kmymoney.org/changelog.html\">Changelog</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"V preteklih izdajah je ta del priročnika vključeval seznam številnih "
"posebnih popravkov napak in funkcionalnih izboljšav. Namesto da te podatke "
"podvajamo, jih lahko najdete neposredno v <ulink url=\"https://kmymoney.org/"
"changelog.html\">dnevniku sprememb</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The 5.0.x and 5.1.x series included some changes needing adjustments on the "
"user's side, if they were upgrading from 4.8.x or an older version. However, "
"we expect that most users have converted to 5.1.x by now. Specifically, "
"there should be no adjustments needed by users converting from 5.1.x to 5.2. "
"If for some reason, you are still using &kmymoney; version 4, you are very "
"strongly encouraged to upgrade, as it is getting increasingly difficult for "
"the team to provide any assistance for very old versions."
msgstr ""
"Seriji 5.0.x in 5.1.x sta vključevali nekaj sprememb, ki so zahtevale "
"prilagoditve na strani uporabnika, če so nadgrajevali s 4.8.x ali starejše "
"različice. Vendar pričakujemo, da je večina uporabnikov do zdaj prešla na "
"5.1.x. Natančneje, pri pretvorbi iz 5.1.x v 5.2 uporabniki ne bi smeli "
"zahtevati nobenih prilagoditev. Če iz nekega razloga še vedno uporabljate "
"&kmymoney; različico 4, vas močno spodbujamo, da nadgradite, saj je ekipi "
"vedno težje zagotoviti kakršno koli pomoč za zelo stare različice."

#. Tag: title
#: whatsnew.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Updates to this Handbook"
msgstr "Posodobitve tega priročnika"

#. Tag: para
#: whatsnew.docbook:48
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section used to present some details related to the lack of a complete "
"handbook update from 4.x to 5.x. As the handbook has now been fully updated "
"for 5.2, this section is no longer necessary."
msgstr ""
"V tem razdelku so bile predstavljene nekatere podrobnosti v zvezi s "
"pomanjkanjem popolne posodobitve priročnika s 4.x na 5.x. Ker je bil "
"priročnik zdaj v celoti posodobljen za 5.2, ta razdelek ni več potreben."

